org.jetel.connection.jdbc

Class SQLScriptParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.connection.jdbc.SQLScriptParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>

    public class SQLScriptParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>
    Splits SQL script into series of SQL statements.
    • Ignores delimiter in comments and strings.
    • Works on Strings, InputStreams and ReadableByteChannels.
    • Removes single-line comments.
    • Keeps multi-line comments
    • Supports optimization hint comments /*! MySQL code here */ or /*+ Oracle code here */
    • Recognizes MySQL double-quote (") strings
    • Supports MySQL quote escaping (\')
    • Strips away whitespace at the beginning of the statement.
    • Throws IOException when input ends unexpectedly or when the underline data source throws IOException.
